<paragraph blockId="3.[714,1248,291,440]" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">
The flowers of 
<taxonomicName box="[910,1116,291,317]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Disperis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humbertii">
<emphasis box="[910,1116,291,317]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Disperis humbertii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from those of 
<taxonomicName box="[805,944,321,348]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Disperis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="anthoceros">
<emphasis box="[805,944,321,348]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">D. anthoceros</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
only in being slightly small- er. In the typical form of 
<taxonomicName box="[983,1124,352,379]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Disperis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="anthoceros">
<emphasis box="[983,1124,352,379]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">D. anthoceros</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the spur is 
<quantity box="[714,833,382,409]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" unit="mm" value="16.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="12.0">12-20 mm</quantity>
long, while in 
<taxonomicName authority="Verdc." authorityName="Verdc." box="[1001,1248,382,409]" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" rank="variety" variety="grandiflora">
var. 
<emphasis box="[1048,1168,383,409]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">grandiflora</emphasis>
Verdc.
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[772,872,414,440]" name="Tanzania" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
, the spur is 
<quantity box="[995,1110,413,440]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.65" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.3" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" unit="mm" value="26.5" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="23.0">23-30 mm</quantity>
long.
</paragraph>
